	<div class="posts">
	<a name="107362012953320857">&nbsp;</a><br>
	<a href="http://tinyscheme.sourceforge.net/home.html">D. Souflis - TinyScheme Download site</a>.&nbsp; Another tiny interpreter system.  I think oMiser will be smaller, but it might do with far fewer data types and not be so speedy too.&nbsp; It will be interesting to see what is included in the weight-watcher version.<br>
	<span class="byline">posted by Dennis at <a href="#107362012953320857">Thursday, January 08, 2004</a></span></div>
