	<a name="107358640026328944">&nbsp;</a><br>
	<a href="http://story.news.yahoo.com/news?tmpl=story&cid=1738&e=2&u=/zd/20040108/tc_zd/115805">Yahoo! News - Gates Salutes the Seamless Computing Experience</a>.&nbsp; So Seamless Experience, Confirmable Experience, and Coherence are related.&nbsp; This is an interesting observation.&nbsp; It will be interesting to see how one can make "Seamless Computing Experience" grounded.&nbsp; I am already concerned about that with regard to confirmable experience.<br>
	<span class="byline">posted by Dennis at <a href="#107358640026328944">Thursday, January 08, 2004</a></span></div>
